<td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>Hey all, I have been talking to some friends about Enchanters and one friend especially is very adament about saying that Enchanters post 60 are useless and serve only as buff-bots since the majority of mobs worth fighting post 60 are all immune to mez.  <br />Now me personally I have played an Ench to 30 and loved every minute of it. But if there is no 'future' in the class beyond being a kei/haste vending machine then forget about it. Thoughts?</p>
